IMAGEMASH
by pops

an image batch processor written in python and pyqt 
with some cool thing such as preview and interactive tools (only one now)

it is released under the GNU GPL V3

the software is in developement and have only one plugin now

Thunar custom action:
xterm -hold -e "python3 /media/donees/programation/imagemash/imagemash.py %F"

